('1d67a975-38ca-4170-88d3-29e79aafff83','SOLD OUT! Vegetarian Tapas Adventure: Flavorful Spanish Small Plates','<p>SOLD OUT! Please check out our other classes! Join Weaver Street Market and our Food House Executive Chef, Glenn Lozuke for an International Culinary Journey to Spain! Dive into this hands-on Vegetarian Tapas Class where Glenn will lead you through delightful recipes and delicious ingredients! Explore the concept and cultural significance of tapas, learn key cooking techniques, and master quick sauces and garnishes that make these wonderful small plates pop! Tickets on sale now!</p>','2026-01-30 23:00:00.000','2026-01-31 01:00:00.000','PAST','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,31543,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/an-international-culinary-journey-hands-on-cooking-class-with-glenn-lozuke/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.934','2026-04-08 18:14:07.628','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
