('5d2d69c7-7097-481e-bd48-3f3eb0c16fe6','Raleigh Wine Fair','<p>Join us for our Raleigh Wine Fair on 4/12 from 3 to 5pm in our Raleigh store!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-300x288.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"288\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-30020\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-300x288.jpg 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-1024x984.jpg 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-768x738.jpg 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-1536x1475.jpg 1536w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-2048x1967.jpg 2048w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/WineSaleandFairs5-600x576.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>','2026-04-12 19:00:00.000','2026-04-12 21:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32153,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/raleigh-wine-fair-3/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.962','2026-04-08 13:48:36.962','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
('5ead7732-8be4-4aea-8bb6-f1ea67fa4bae','Piedmont Farm Tour','<p>The&nbsp;Piedmont&nbsp;Farm&nbsp;Tour&nbsp;is&nbsp;back&nbsp;for&nbsp;its&nbsp;29th&nbsp;year!</p><p>Every&nbsp;spring,&nbsp;local&nbsp;farmers&nbsp;open&nbsp;their&nbsp;gates&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;behind-the-scenes&nbsp;look&nbsp;at&nbsp;how&nbsp;local&nbsp;food&nbsp;is&nbsp;grown.&nbsp;Meet&nbsp;the&nbsp;farmers,&nbsp;explore&nbsp;working&nbsp;farms,&nbsp;and&nbsp;experience&nbsp;sustainable&nbsp;agriculture&nbsp;firsthand—all&nbsp;in&nbsp;one&nbsp;unforgettable&nbsp;weekend.</p><p>Tour&nbsp;Buttons&nbsp;One&nbsp;button&nbsp;gives&nbsp;you&nbsp;access&nbsp;to&nbsp;all&nbsp;participating&nbsp;farms&nbsp;all&nbsp;weekend&nbsp;long.</p><p>&nbsp;•&nbsp;$35&nbsp;in&nbsp;advance&nbsp;|&nbsp;$40&nbsp;day&nbsp;of&nbsp;tour</p><p>&nbsp;•&nbsp;$25&nbsp;for&nbsp;CFSA&nbsp;or&nbsp;Weaver&nbsp;Street&nbsp;Market&nbsp;members.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/ed9ebe7d-dc0c-4310-a21d-bd4696e1be5e/r/Rn7tlMc4skuMJfZVxqMDAAgAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fwww.weaverstreetmarket.coop%252Fget-involved%252Fbecome-an-owner-online%252F%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&amp;msdynmkt_digest=Fr%2B%2FOkoYMNhjAYTSTGmMss20y6LYHblgQ2cwRLDjvS0%3D&amp;msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Become&nbsp;on&nbsp;Owner</a>&nbsp;today!</p><p>Buttons&nbsp;and&nbsp;Maps&nbsp;are&nbsp;available&nbsp;at&nbsp;all&nbsp;Weaver&nbsp;Street&nbsp;Market&nbsp;locations&nbsp;beginning&nbsp;April&nbsp;3,&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/ed9ebe7d-dc0c-4310-a21d-bd4696e1be5e/r/Rn7tlMc4skuMJfZVxqMDAAkAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22http%253A%252F%252Fcarolinafarmstewards.org%252Fpiedmont-farm-tour%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&amp;msdynmkt_digest=XG%2FAhiOOD3ZvXcT5LOihBPJ6d15F3mSYIzrVVU7iMbI%3D&amp;msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">onlin</a>e.</p><p>Preview&nbsp;the&nbsp;tour&nbsp;brochure&nbsp;<a href=\"https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/ed9ebe7d-dc0c-4310-a21d-bd4696e1be5e/r/Rn7tlMc4skuMJfZVxqMDAAoAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22http%253A%252F%252Fheyzine.com%252Fflip-book%252Fcfsa-pft-2026-brochure%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&amp;msdynmkt_digest=I3u260ODWuCvKFy8EmH%2FUofzYTCVD6AK0LLwUVWxejo%3D&amp;msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/ed9ebe7d-dc0c-4310-a21d-bd4696e1be5e/r/Rn7tlMc4skuMJfZVxqMDAAwAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22http%253A%252F%252Fsignup.com%252Fclient%252Finvitation2%252Fsecure%252F623464482013%252Ffalse%2523%252Finvitation%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%220%22%3Anull%7D%7D&amp;msdynmkt_digest=CIZa3qnSbrpNVeLu0hKTKpsHEhX4X4n1Xi0gKT21rWU%3D&amp;msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Volunteer</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;tour&nbsp;for&nbsp;free!&nbsp;Volunteers&nbsp;receive&nbsp;a&nbsp;limited-edition&nbsp;t-shirt&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;free&nbsp;tour&nbsp;pass.</p><p>Thank&nbsp;you&nbsp;for&nbsp;supporting&nbsp;local&nbsp;farms.</p><p><a href=\"https://carolinafarmstewards.org/piedmont-farm-tour/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Piedmont&nbsp;Farm&nbsp;Tour&nbsp;–&nbsp;Carolina&nbsp;Farm&nbsp;Stewardship&nbsp;Association</a></p>','2026-04-25 18:00:00.000','2026-04-26 22:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','27aab117-6037-4ab7-8df1-b15509456f27','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32420,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/piedmont-farm-tour-10/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.969','2026-04-08 19:12:24.483','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','4b272e69-913e-428c-ac0c-8f3431600bca','<p></p>'),
