('69c32e4d-606b-4665-965a-1b1047a1fa74','SOLD OUT! Sip  Create: Floral Arranging with Split Acre Farms','<p>SOLD OUT! Please check out our other events! Join us for a glass of wine and an evening of floral arranging with Split Acre Farms! Learn the secrets of floral arranging and take home your own bouquet! This event is the perfect pre-Valentine&#8217;s Day outing for your special someone! Tickets on sale now!</p>','2026-02-08 22:00:00.000','2026-02-09 00:00:00.000','PAST','f62716b6-696d-4431-965d-64a485eb172e','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,31551,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/sip-create-floral-arranging-with-split-acre-farms/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.936','2026-04-08 18:14:07.628','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
