('7002d6e7-453c-4016-be04-0342057992f5','Raleigh Lunch  Learn: Getting to the Heart of Cardiovascular Disease: A Natural Approach to Prevention and Solutions','<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/rodney-mcbride-photo-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/rodney-mcbride-photo-1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-31853 alignleft\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/rodney-mcbride-photo-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/rodney-mcbride-photo-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/rodney-mcbride-photo-1-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/rodney-mcbride-photo-1-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/rodney-mcbride-photo-1.jpg 481w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><span data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\">Come and grab lunch with us at our Raleigh store and join us in the upstairs cafe for a free Lunch &amp; Learn on &#8220;Getting to the Heart of Cardiovascular Disease: A Natural Approach to Prevention and Solutions.&#8221; Presenter Dr. Rodney Mcbride is a chiropractor based in Raleigh, NC. He has seventeen years of diverse experience in chiropractic and specialization in Applied Kinesiology, Functional Nutrition, and Muscle Testing. Dr. Mcbride is known for his holistic approach to health, which includes the use of nutrition and lifestyle changes to restore balance and health. <a href=\"https://www.bagofboneschiropractic.com/\">Chiropractic | Bag Of Bones Chiropractic | Raleigh</a></span></p>','2026-02-26 16:00:00.000','2026-02-26 17:30:00.000','PAST','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,31852,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/raleigh-lunch-learn-getting-to-the-heart-of-cardiovascular-disease-a-natural-approach-to-prevention-and-solutions/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.938','2026-04-08 18:14:07.628','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
