('78c2c385-f482-4ff4-aa8d-3de1d526febe','Silent Book Club at Weaver Street Market','<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-32492 alignleft\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/iStock-2206406623.jpg 1732w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Join us with your favorite book, grab a coffee, tea or cold drink (snack or dinner from our food bar too!) and join us in our upstairs cafe area where you can find your own table, grab a private space on our balcony, or share your table with others!  Do you have already loved and read books you&#8217;d like to swap for &#8220;new to you&#8221; books?  Bring them with you and we&#8217;ll have a table set up for swapping!</p>\n<div class=\"mceTemp\"></div>','2026-04-08 21:00:00.000','2026-04-08 23:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,3249