('884274ed-a57a-4a17-a9ff-eb9c0ab85cde','Pizza Making Class','<p><span>Join us at </span><strong>Weaver Street Market</strong><span> for a fun and laid-back </span><strong>pizza making class</strong><span>! Whether you&#8217;re a newbie or a pizza pro, Weaver Street Market Bread Bakery Manager, Jon McDonald, will teach you how to craft delicious pies from scratch. We&#8217;ll meet on </span><strong>June 5, 2026 at 6:00 PM</strong><span>. Bring your appetite and get ready to toss some dough with friends!</span></p>','2026-06-05 19:00:00.000','2026-06-05 21:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32282,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/pizza-making-class/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.990','2026-04-08 13:48:36.990','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
('899966a4-610e-4f12-8074-3a8ff63c7dd8','Spring Coop Fair on the Carrboro Lawn','<p>Join us for our Spring Coop Fair on the Carrboro Lawn! On May 3rd from 2 to 5pm!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i-300x269.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"269\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-26359\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i-300x269.jpg 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i-1024x916.jpg 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i-768x687.jpg 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i-1536x1375.jpg 1536w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i-600x537.jpg 600w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_i.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_a.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_a-236x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"236\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-26356\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_a-236x300.jpg 236w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_a-806x1024.jpg 806w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_a-768x976.jpg 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_a-600x763.jpg 600w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/CoopFair_a.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 236px) 100vw, 236px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Co