('8f0284d6-9efe-47d3-8ed8-50720c8e2e1f','Carrboro Wine Fair','<p>Join us for our Carrboro Spring Wine Fair on April 4th from 3 to 5pm on our Carrboro lawn!</p>','2026-04-04 19:00:00.000','2026-04-04 21:00:00.000','PAST','7b0ecc8b-704c-4df4-9128-53e85ac7e1cd','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32131,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/carrboro-wine-fair-3/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.952','2026-04-08 18:14:07.628','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
('90a6f684-943f-4d5c-85df-73dfb9afca1d','Sourdough Bread Class','<p>TWO SPACES LEFT! Check out our other events! Join us at our Raleigh store on March 6th from 6 to 8pm for a Sourdough Bread Class led by Weaver Street Market&#8217;s own Bread Bakery Manager Jon McDonald! Flour, water, and salt. That’s all you need to make tasty, nutritious bread at home. Spend two hours with Jon learning how to maintain a sourdough starter, how to mix and shape dough, and how to bake your own bread at home. Students will leave with recipes, some Weaver Street starter, and dough they’ve mixed to jumpstart their own sourdough journey.</p>','2026-03-06 23:00:00.000','2026-03-07 01:00:00.000','PAST','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,31549,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/sourdough-bread-class/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.943','2026-04-08 18:14:07.628','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
('91cd1844-4cb8-4777-93c1-5216ed242b4a','Pasta Making Class','<p><span>Join us in our Raleigh Upstairs Tasting Kitchen for a hands-on pasta making class! Learn the basics of making hand-rolled and cut pasta and a few simple and delicious ways to sauce it! Tickets on sale now!</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Pasta.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Pasta-300x259.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"259\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-23211\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Pasta-300x259.jpg 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Pasta-1024x883.jpg 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Pasta-600x518.jpg 600w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Pasta.jpg 1639w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>','2026-04-25 22:00:00.000','2026-04-26 00:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32155,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/pasta-making-class/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.971','2026-04-08 13:48:36.971','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
('932a7978-22d0-46e5-8797-fc74f335a345','Raleigh Friday Night Tasting Event','<p>Join us for samplings in our Raleigh store on Friday nights from 5 to 7pm!<a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-scaled.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-279x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"279\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-32135\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-279x300.png 279w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-953x1024.png 953w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-768x825.png 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-1430x1536.png 1430w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-1907x2048.png 1907w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Friday-night-Tastings-RL-SOCIAL-2-600x644.png 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 279px) 100vw, 279px\" /></a></p>','2026-05-15 21:00:00.000','2026-05-15 23:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32142,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/raleigh-friday-night-tasting-event-2/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.978','2026-04-08 13:48:36.978','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
('957fc34c-2d3f-4e8a-8806-83761795c04d','Living History: From the Rock Wall (New Date)','<p><span data-teams=\"true\">In celebration of Black History Month, we are collaborating with the Marian Cheek Jackson Center for the 3rd year to share the stories of Chapel Hill and Carrboro&#8217;s Black history. The Marian Cheek Jackson Center is a public history non-profit that works to honor the legacy of historic Black neighborhoods, Black history, and advocate for housing justice.<br />\nLearn local history through the voices of local poets, speakers, and historians. This free event invites you to explore the legacy and impact of the historic Northside, Pine Knolls, and Tin Top neighborhoods, offering personal narratives from significant moments in local history. Come sample food from local Black-owned businesses whose products we carry at our stores. Everyone is welcome to join us in this meaningful celebration!</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-6.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-6-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-32073 size-medium\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-6-300x300.png 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-6-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-6-150x150.png 150w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-6-768x768.png 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-6-200x200.png 200w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-Hi