('9f0cc683-a64b-4558-8879-fbde0a709834','Beyond Salad: Fun Meal Prep for the Week','<p><span>Join us at </span><strong>Weaver Street Market</strong><span> on </span><strong>May 29, 2026 at 6:00 PM </strong><span>for a fun and easy meal prep session! Say goodbye to boring salads and learn creative ways to prep your meals for the week ahead. Perfect for anyone who loves tasty food without the hassle. Bring your appetite and get ready to make meal prep something you actually look forward to with Weaver Street Market Executive Chef Glenn Lozuke! Tickets on sale now!</span></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_14153\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14153\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/pot-pies-by-glenn.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/pot-pies-by-glenn-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"Glenn holding tray of pot pies by oven\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-14153\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/pot-pies-by-glenn-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/pot-pies-by-glenn-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/pot-pies-by-glenn-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/pot-pies-by-glenn.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-14153\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Glenn bakes pot pies</figcaption></figure>','2026-05-29 22:00:00.000','2026-05-30 00:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','d3ea6f92-2fd4-4134-9d28-622256b37d42','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32270,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/beyond-salad-fun-meal-prep-for-the-week/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.986','2026-04-08 13:48:36.986','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',N