('a120e5b4-e6de-4f92-a194-4b9890e46595','Italian Cheese  Wine Pop Up  Hillsborough','<p><span>Join us at </span><strong>Weaver Street Market in Hillsborough</strong><span> on </span><strong>June 7, 2026 at 3:00 PM </strong><span> for a chill afternoon of tasting some amazing </span><strong>Italian cheeses</strong><span> and </span><strong>wines</strong><span>. It’s the perfect chance to discover new flavors, chat with fellow food lovers, and enjoy a relaxed vibe. Don’t miss out on this tasty pop-up event — see you there! Tickets available now! Two sessions &#8211; 3pm to 4pm and 4pm to 5pm.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-32262\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/iStock-185185623-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>','2026-06-07 19:00:00.000','2026-06-07 21:00:00.000','SCHEDULED','f62716b6-696d-4431-965d-64a485eb172e','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL,32268,'https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/event/italian-cheese-wine-pop-up-hillsborough/','2026-04-08 13:48:36.993','2026-04-08 13:48:36.993','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7','b0e75286-eb68-4763-b237-37363ed93aa7',NULL),
